data.name: RESPIRATORY MASKS
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- 100% PVC and 100% DEHP-FREE PVC

## STERILIZATION
- Ethylene Oxide (EO) Sterile

## PRESENTATIONS
- Soft PVC and DEHP-FREE PVC
- Adjustable Nose Clip
- Transparent and Transparent/Green Color
- Adult, Paediatric, Infant and Neonate
- Adult and Paediatric

## PERFORMANCE
- Soft Materials
- Comfortable by Wearing
